" Cursor movement
nmap <C-k> 3k
xmap <C-k> 3k
nmap <C-j> 3j
xmap <C-h> ^
nmap <C-l> $
xmap <C-l> $
xmap <C-j> 3j
nmap <C-h> ^
nmap <C-S-k> 10k
xmap <C-S-k> 10k
nmap <C-S-j> 10j
xmap <C-S-j> 10j

" Screen movement
nnoremap <C-n> 3<C-e>
vnoremap <C-n> 3<C-e>
nnoremap <C-p> 3<C-y>
vnoremap <C-p> 3<C-y>
nnoremap <C-f> <C-d>
vnoremap <C-f> <C-d>
nnoremap <C-d> <C-u>
vnoremap <C-d> <C-u>

" Move Visual block (Indent, Outdent)
vmap > >gv
vmap < <gv

